    <title>제니스코퍼레이션 이미지 뷰어</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
